## 5 Carat Emerald Cut Diamond Ring Price

A natural 5ct emerald cut diamond ring is not a mainstream purchase — it is a collector-level stone at every price point. Six GIA-certified natural emerald cuts at or near 5ct are available in current certified market data, ranging from $121,475 to $251,745 for the stone alone.

The range within the natural 5ct category is wider than at smaller sizes. The same carat weight carries a $130,000 spread depending on color and clarity grades — D-VS1 at $121,475 versus D-IF at $245,156. The step-cut shape amplifies the difference between grades because every grade is visible in the stone's wide open table at 12mm × 9mm.

