The [ten prong solitaire at $860](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/ten-prong-solitaire-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-by-james-allen-item-311235?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) is the most common choice at 5ct because it disappears under the stone — four small prongs, plain shank, nothing competing with the 12mm table above. At this size, the stone is the ring; the setting exists only to hold it. A [bezel setting at $4,300](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/bezel-set-emerald-cut-side-stone-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-by-james-allen-item-304632?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) adds full edge protection with baguette side stones that complement the rectangular step-cut center — the step-cut's sharp corners are the most vulnerable part of an emerald cut, and at 5ct they extend further from center, increasing daily exposure.

[![Emerald cut diamond engagement ring white gold solitaire pavé band on hand](https://ion.bluenile.com/sets/Jewelry/Photoshoot/Bluenile/BrioSuperImposeBox/Rings/505031/505031_M1_EMR_DIM_wht_0100CT_W_Box2_004_1600X1600.jpg)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings?MetalType=all&Diamonds=Dia&ShapeID=Emerald&a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)

Platinum is the right metal at 5ct for both natural and lab stones. At this size, the ring will be worn daily, and eventual resizing needs to be done carefully. Platinum does not wear thin the way 14K gold does — it is denser, the prongs maintain their grip over years, and a platinum setting for a $120,000 stone is a worthwhile additional investment. The [platinum bezel with side stones at $4,625](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/bezel-set-emerald-cut-side-stone-diamond-engagement-ring-in-platinum-by-james-allen-item-304637?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) is the right setting for any natural 5ct stone over $100,000. The [$340 difference between 14K white gold and platinum](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/bezel-set-emerald-cut-side-stone-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-by-james-allen-item-304632?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) at that price level is not a meaningful economy.

For the full range of emerald cut settings see [emerald cut diamond ring settings](/emerald-cut-diamond-ring-settings).

