## 5 Carat Lab Grown Emerald Cut Diamond Ring

The lab-grown 5ct emerald cut market is the most price-diverse segment in the entire lab diamond category. The same carat weight spans from [$8,210](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/28857918?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) to [$49,333](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/27423677?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) for the stone alone. That $41,000 spread is driven by certification lab and grade — E-VVS1 IGI at the low end, GIA D-FL at the high end.

